node.text:
Say hello to FLY Racing's 2022 moto gear line!
 
Combining the latest in style and protection, this line up is one for the books! 
 
The 2022 collection continues to innovate in technology, too! Featuring durable stretch materials, BOA Fit Systems and revolutionary RHEON Technology, expectations have been redefined. 
 
Work hard, play harder with FLY Racing '22.
 
#FlyRacing #FlyRacingFamily #FlyFormula #FLYRacing2022

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Joey Savatgy on July 18, 2021 tagging @flyracingusa, @ridedunlop, @teamrmatvmc, and @alpinestarsmx. May be an image of dirt bike, motorcycle and outdoors.

node.text: It’s been a tough go lately but things are going in the right direction. Felt good this weekend, unfortunate crash in turn 1 but 11-7. Back to work 👨🏼‍✈️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Joey Savatgy on June 20, 2021 tagging @alpinestars, @flyracingusa, @ridedunlop, and @teamrmatvmc. May be an image of motorcycle, dirt bike and outdoors.

node.text: 8-9 for P9.. better weekend, qualifying was good. All In all built the foundation so I’m happy 👊🏽

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Joey Savatgy on June 06, 2021 tagging @flyracingusa, @ridedunlop, @teamrmatvmc, and @alpinestarsmx. May be an image of motorcycle, dirt bike and outdoors.

node.text: Moto 1 10th after a poor start. Moto 2 got a much better start but unfortunately had a rear brake issue starting on lap 2.. not a fun track to ride with no rear brake. But overall riding was better this weekend so take the positives and keep moving 🙏🏽

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Joey Savatgy on May 30, 2021. May be an image of motorcycle, dirt bike and outdoors.

node.text: Round 1 was far from ideal. 12th in moto 1 after a really slow first half of the race. Crashed twice second moto, healthy just bummed on the mistakes. Back to work

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Joey Savatgy on May 19, 2021. May be an image of motorcycle, dirt bike and text.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Joey Savatgy on May 09, 2021 tagging @_megansavatgy. May be an image of 2 people, child and people standing.

node.text: Happy Mother’s Day babe. You’re the best, I love watching you transform into the badass do it all mom you are. River and I are so thankful for everything you do for us ❤️❤️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Joey Savatgy on May 07, 2021. May be an image of motorcycle and outdoors.
Photo shared by Joey Savatgy on May 03, 2021 tagging @alpinestars, @flyracingusa, @ridedunlop, and @teamrmatvmc. May be an image of motorcycle, dirt bike and outdoors.

node.text: Round 17 P6.. felt good to finish on a high note, the last 2 rounds really clicked for me. Happy with the progress I made from round 1 to now. Onto MX 🤝

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Joey Savatgy on April 25, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, motorcycle and outdoors.

node.text: Well. Last night was frustrating to say the least, asked too much out of what the track was giving. But yesterday was big for me. Made some changes on the bike before the weekend and felt like the old 17! Fast all day, and steps in the right direction. Nice little soil sample Thursday too 🤒
